==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: pepperwood
<hw>pepperwood</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A Pacific coast tree
(<spn>Umbellularia californica</spn>) having aromatic foliage and small
umbellate flowers followed by olivelike fruit; yields a hard tough
wood.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> California laurel, California bay tree, Oregon
myrtle, spice tree, sassafras laurel, California olive, mountain laurel,
Umbellularia californica.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pepperwort</ent>⟦br⟧
